| Plan | Pages/month | Price |
|------|-------------|-------|
| Free | 2,000 | $0 (no credit card) |
| Pro | 50,000 | $99/mo |
| Scale | Custom | Custom pricing |

Response headers: `X-RateLimit-Limit`, `X-RateLimit-Remaining`, `X-RateLimit-Used`, `X-RateLimit-Reset`

